name: That API Meetup: REST, Cloud Integrations & SaaS :Sydney, AU
description:
We've joined forces with our fellow Australian API enthusiasts for a series of virtual Meetups. The first is something that represents a huge opportunity for consumers, startups and enterprise alike - the requirement from February 2020 for the Big Four banks to provide access to consumer data via APIs.

Who better to kick off than Eyal Sivan aka Mr Open Banking https://www.mropenbanking.com/

Followed up by subject matter expert in James Bligh from Data61 https://www.linkedin.com/in/jamesbligh/?originalSubdomain=au

All facilitated by API evangelist, Uli Hitzel to keep the event running smoothly and ensure that there is plenty of opportunity for peer interaction.

Date & Time:
- Friday the 29th - 12noon – 1:30pm - A great lunchtime event!

How to watch:
- Youtube Live stream
- Zoom

To register for this event and the connection details use the Eventbrite link below;

https://www.eventbrite.com.au/e/apis-across-australia-cdr-vs-open-banking-tickets-105340040898
